phrases: Back then we tried to fly with propellers that could not do it
We ran with bare feet, and now we see different skies
What are you waiting for, Madoka?!
We have to get out of here!
Something unexpected must have interfered during the fusion
of Lady Yurikano and Kyono Madoka's personalities,
which might be the because of this anomaly
I will hear your explanation later.
Get Yurikano off the ship to safety.
Right now, we have to run!
It is too dangerous to remain on board!
You must head to the escape pod immediately!
We will escort you, Lady Yurikano.
There is something I have to tell you!
You, and you, all of you...
You all need to stop right this instant!
The surrounding energy field is in flux.
Could that be what is causing the anomaly on Dizelmine's ship?
We came here to get Yurikano back.
What happens to the Le Garite vessel is none of our concern
The Eques are about to intercept them.
Perhaps they are using a new type of weapon against us.
Send out every Ovid we have available to attack!
Where could Madoka and Muginami be?
Currently unable to guarantee that the launch systems will function properly.
All Ovids are to launch using manual launch protocols.
Our sensors have picked up multiple Ovid launches
Are you still going to tell me
that this war is just between
Do not mind if I do.
Just do not get in my way!
I have to return to the lab!
The anomaly is assuredly because I have returned to this world!
I need to use the Vox Core and return beyond the Rinne immediately!
What is gotten into you, Madoka?!
I keep telling you, I am not
they must have spiked your drink with something nasty!
Hold on, this is my chance!
That is right, my name is Yurikano.
I may not look it, but I am indeed the princess of De Metrio.
I, the most regal one, hereby command you.
I request an audience with Lan's brother immediately!
I need to stop this fighting already...
First, we detect a powerful energy field...
Next, the Vox just flies off by themselves.
What the hell's going on up there?
The anomaly was seen originating from the Le Garite flagship.
We have confirmed link-ups with Lympha and Ignis.
Which means Lan and Muginami are safe.
Well, the signal indicates it is made contact with the pilot.
I see, so you are hers...
Take me to the laboratory division of this ship.
The Vox will not respond unless both mind and body are united as one.
I need to tell Lan's brother something really important!
If we survive this, we can make it to Dizelmine's ship!
If we do not hurry, Yurikano's life will be in danger.
Why did that Le Garite Ovid save me?!
Did not I teach you that it is not the enemy,
but your own carelessness that trips you up?
It is a long story, but I am stuck in her body.
Hey, that is a pretty lame joke if you ask me!
was something Yurikano's said to me countless times.
And Madoka would not know our tactical radio frequency.
You really expect me to believe that?!
What about that time during the Academy's drill camp?!
I was bathing and I saw a mouse,
a-and clung to you stark naked, remember?!
Let us take out those guys first!
Do not go on the defensive!
Drive a wedge into their formation before you are surrounded!
What we do know is that the pilot is extremely skilled.
Our standard squadron is no match.
It took me an entire minute just to deal with those amateurs.
Did I get rusty while stuck inside the Rinne all that time?
Time for the elite squad now, eh?
You believed that even royalty should know how to cook for themselves.
I could make all sorts of dishes just by guessing the ingredients
and every time you ate my cooking you would tell me
how important measuring and following the recipe was!
I wonder if this thing is carrying any food.
I could go for some fish-flavored crackers.
Crackers and a bottle of Kamogawa Energy would be perfect...
I am going to die of hunger before I even get to Le Garite.
I wish there was some way for me
to tell Lan's brother and Giuvi
But I wonder why she does not want to tell them herself?
I totally do not get it...
If his ship's so messed up that he cannot come out,
I will go and meet him from the inside!
I, Fin E Ld Si Laffinty, Princess of Le Garite, command you!
What is with this Brother stuff?
I keep telling you, I am not her!
Brother, what have you done to Makoka?
Do not look at me with such a sad face!
What can I do to make you people believe me?!
S-Sweet and sour pork... E-Edible hot chili oil... Y-Y...
I really do not get why Miss Yurikano does not want to tell
Lan's brother and Big Brother Giuvi how she feels.
If she tells them, they might even understand...
I mean, it sounds pretty simple enough to me.
She has to take her sweet time
like a girl hesitating to confess to some guy she loves.
I-I am in love with you...
Yurikano just could not stand it.
Seeing her brother and the man she loved
trying to duke it out all the time.
Sacrificing herself probably did not hurt as much.
Well, that is the last of the rations.
If some day, I could meet Lan's brother again...
I want to tell him how you feel.
Does not look like that day will ever come.
Why will not you respond to my commands?
Is it because I am not in my own body?
No. Right now you are Miss Madoka, are not you?
Being able to fly Aura implies
that you did indeed swap places with her.
I am back in my own body.
Madoka, I thought you were in the escape pod.
Then she must be back there now?!
When I see the flowers of Lagrange in full bloom like this,
of the day when Yurikano and I became engaged.
We were so little that we hardly knew the meaning of that word.
But we were entrusted to become the guidepost
for Le Garite and De Metrio to work together and move forward.
As time passed, our two planets parted ways,
and in a similar manner, the ties that bound us were severed.
Even then, the love I felt for her never faded.
To this day, I still love Yurikano.
That is why my heart aches.
This chaos is necessary for the billions of citizens in the Polyhedron.
It is hard to imagine that the person you love would not understand.
I do not want to hate Yurikano.
I want her to share my feelings.
If she really does love me...
Why do not you ask her directly?
Do not get the wrong idea!
I would never love a man like him!
So go right ahead and hate me.
If that means that this world will not be buried in grief...
If that is what it takes...
I will have to let you go.
Be honest, do not you think all men are fools?
If by some miracle we get the chance...
Let us have a nice, long talk.
I will come to see you, Yurikano.
I wanted you more than anyone to understand these feelings.
I did not want you, of all people, to know about them.
I have been wavering back and forth between these feelings...
Is that what it means to love someone?
and wanting them to understand yours...
But if you cannot understand that,
I will have to teach you the hard way!

On the water's surface I see a light reflected that stirs my heart
we were already deeply connected under the blue sky
We had so much fun, as in a daze, that time seemed forgotten
I prayed that there would be no end to the way we lived
I will not forget our days together, although time goes by,
and you are far from me now,
because you left behind a wonderful world
